        "avatar": "7e64e4a94789309cc57c75fc7ff1d518eea0bd48"
      },
      "language": "english",
      "review": "It's extremely hard to even find a starting point when it comes to praising this game, It is one of the most perfect, characterized, polished, Indie RPG Farming Sims ever made. For the price tag being as low as it is, with the amount of content, love, and care put into this game by the creator, It is a no brainer to pick this game up whenever you get the chance. This game gets free updates and patches that would be seen by triple A companies as DLC, ConcernedApe has basically bled into this game so much that it has become their firstborn child, it has such a cute and wholesome style with an addictive day to night cycle where you get locked in for hours completing chores, tasks, and upgrades you look forward to, all while building relationships and learning about the town, it is such a fun grind and gameplay loop. The fishing mechanics in this game has inspired so many other games because of how much fun it is and how simple it can also be. This is the cornerstone of Indie Farming Sims for the enjoyers of the genre, a must play in every category. When ConcernedApe releases Haunted Chocolatier it might actually be the best Pixel RPG Life Sim to exist. Please release Haunted Chocolatier.",
